'''Manta Ray''' is a {{Rarity|Mythical}} fish found in [[Roslit Bay]].

== Description ==
{{Description|Manta Rays are very elegant and remarkably large creatures that coast alongside the coral reefs of Roslit Bay. They move their wing-like fins in a wavy motion to generate enough speed to guide through the ocean. Manta Rays typically feed on small fish during the night.|Bestiary Entry}}

